    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Click inside the groupbox with right or left mouse button to see how the event is been handled.<br />The label in the groupbox shows&nbsp;which mouse button was clicked.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The <em>GroupBox </em>contains Click event that is fired when user clicks on the <em>GroupBox </em>with the mouse button.</p>]]></Paragraph>
